br />\n我既觀察係2月6號開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唯有盡量多d表達多d發聲， <br />\n表達多d自己睇法。</blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇翻原來2月6號星期一 就係一個禮拜前， 同你吻合。<br />\n<br />\n我係用觀察+數據去推測既。"},{"pid":"ef498e23db97258e9188ac642ef1ff80bd3de68e","tid":111963,"uid":59695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>五毛活動呢個禮拜明顯增加</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越嚟越多架喇，<br />\n<br />\n我既觀察係2月6號開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唯有盡量多d表達多d發聲， <br />\n表達多d自己睇法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當每次去同五毛作對其實就係同「其他國家」嘅國家資源對抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n養五毛仲用得多錢過國防.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9226834b5b5f76c081fe157bf2f9d56690049cb","tid":111963,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea9a80f32bd999961f47e8e440d018436b67a04","tid":111963,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9ad245a2c245598d2dd4cb891f22d6138aeac6","tid":111963,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"351464bef6011bfa89940f602111348cb7defb2e","tid":111963,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T19:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa761137ec872e3525f45e637dec13a04a99973","tid":111963,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個POST 應該